OL,3,CHome Secretary warns against division
OL,4,Cover Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FHome Secretary Shabana Mahmood has
OL,7,Fcondemned the murder of Southampton
OL,8,Fstudent Henry Nowak as an "evil act"
OL,9,Fas she told the Commons, "we cannot
OL,10,Fallow this murder to turn communities
OL,11,Fagainst one another".
OL,13,FMr Nowak's killer, 23-year-old Vickrum
OL,14,FDigwa, told police attending the scene
OL,15,Fof the stabbing in Southampton on
OL,16,FDecember 3, 2025, that he had been the
OL,17,Fvictim of a racist attack.
OL,26,@pD@[OUpD@dO]qD@ZOUsD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780481194
OL,3,CHome Secretary warns against division
OL,4,Cover Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FBody-worn camera footage from the
OL,7,Fincident appeared to show Mr Nowak,
OL,8,Fwho had received two stab wounds on
OL,9,Fthe back of his legs and a fatal wound
OL,10,Fto his heart, repeatedly pleading
OL,11,F"I've been stabbed" and "I can't
OL,12,Fbreathe" while being handcuffed.
OL,14,FThe harrowing case has prompted
OL,15,Fwidespread anger over the 18-year-
OL,16,Fold's treatment by police officers as
OL,17,Fhe lay dying and the 21-year sentence
OL,18,Fhanded to Digwa on Monday.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@SO]sD@YOUtD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780481194
OL,3,CHome Secretary warns against division
OL,4,Cover Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,7,FConduct (IOPC) said investigators, who
OL,8,Fwill meet Mr Nowak's family, are
OL,9,Fexamining a large amount of body-worn
OL,10,Fvideo as well as material presented
OL,11,Fduring Digwa's trial. The watchdog is
OL,12,Fplanning to report on the police
OL,13,Fhandling of Henry Nowak's murder in
OL,14,Fthe next three months, Mahmood said.
OL,16,FOn Tuesday morning, Nigel Farage
OL,17,Fissued a statement about the case,
OL,18,Fsuggesting that we are "living in two-
OL,19,Ftier Britain where the rights and
OL,20,Fprivileges of white people matter less
OL,21,Fthan those of ethnic minorities".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780481194
OL,3,CHome Secretary warns against division
OL,4,Cover Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FThe Home Secretary condemned those
OL,7,F"who seek personal political profit
OL,8,Ffrom tragedy".
OL,10,FContinuing her statement, Mahmood
OL,11,Freinforced the government's commitment
OL,12,Fto halving knife crime but admitted:
OL,13,F"We must do more whilst there are
OL,14,Fstill tragedies like this one".
OL,16,FShe said a "dangerous undercurrent" in
OL,17,Fthe wake of Mr Nowak's murder has led
OL,18,Fto death threats against police.
OL,26,@xD@LOUxD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30705
