OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780481194
OL,3,CHome Secretary warns against division
OL,4,Cover Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FLabour MP Tanmanjeet Singh Dhesi has
OL,7,Faccused Reform UK and Restore Britain
OL,8,Fof politicising pain and using the
OL,9,FSikh community as a "scapegoat".
OL,11,FThe MP for Slough said he was "deeply
OL,12,Fsaddened by the murder of Henry Nowak".
OL,14,FHe continued: "What's very galling is
OL,15,Fthat the likes of Reform, Restore, and
OL,16,Fthe far-right decided to politicise
OL,17,Fpeople's pain, attacking the Sikh
OL,18,Fcommunity for wearing the kirpan and
OL,19,Fwanting it banned, even though the
OL,20,Fkirpan was not used in this violent
OL,21,Fattack.
OL,26,@qD@UOUqD@_O]sD@_OUtD@fO]vD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780481194
OL,3,CHome Secretary warns against division
OL,4,Cover Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,F"And they've decided to scapegoat and
OL,7,Fthrow under the bus an entire
OL,8,Fcommunity based on the actions of one
OL,9,Fviolent murderer."
OL,11,FSpeaking to broadcasters on Tuesday
OL,12,Fafternoon, Nigel Farage said he "feels
OL,13,Fa sense of cold rage" about the case
OL,14,Fand claimed that Hampshire police are
OL,15,Ftold "to police incidents differently
OL,16,Faccording to ethnicity".
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
