OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780481194
OL,3,CHome Secretary warns against division
OL,4,Cover Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FThe Speaker, Sir Lindsay Hoyle,
OL,7,Fordered the government to give a
OL,8,Fstatement on this case following
OL,9,Fpublic and political outcry about
OL,10,FDigwa's trial, who was jailed for
OL,11,Flife, with a minimum sentence of 21
OL,12,Fyears, on Monday.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
