OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780481194
OL,3,CHome Secretary warns against division
OL,4,Cover Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FSpeaking at his Cabinet meeting on
OL,7,FTuesday morning, the prime minister
OL,8,Fsaid Nowak's life "had been ripped
OL,9,Faway in the most appalling
OL,10,Fcircumstances" and that his killer
OL,11,F"had shamelessly lied".
OL,13,FHe added that it was right that the
OL,14,FIOPC were investigating the response
OL,15,Fand urged that it be carried out as
OL,16,Fquickly as possible and that answers
OL,17,Fbe delivered.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
